25 LC 129 0002
House Resolution 15
By: Representative Williamson of the 112th
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating Howard "Sonny" Turner upon his induction into the Georgia Association of
2 Conservation Districts' Hall of Fame; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Howard "Sonny" Turner has long been recognized by his peers and colleagues
4 as an individual who has made extraordinary contributions to soil and water conservation in
5 the state; and
6 WHEREAS, his upbringing on a dairy farm inspired a deep, lifelong commitment to
7 Georgia's conservation efforts, beginning with his attendance at the state's first ever Natural
8 Resources Conservation Workshop in 1962 and his graduation from the University of
9 Georgia in agricultural education; and
10 WHEREAS, he has served as the district supervisor representing Walton County's
11 Conservation District for 14 years, serves as vice president on the Georgia Association of
12 Conservation Districts' board, and was awarded Supervisor of the Year in 2023 for
13 outstanding leadership throughout his region; and
