14 WHEREAS, Howard "Sonny" Turner has further dedicated innumerable hours of his time
15 and energy to educating youth through volunteering for the local 4-H program and serving
16 in leadership roles for several civic and educational organizations; and
17 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this remarkable individual be
18 appropriately recognized.
19 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
20 the members of this body congratulate Howard "Sonny" Turner upon his induction into the
21 Georgia Association of Conservation Districts' Hall of Fame as well as extend sincere best
22 wishes for future health, happiness, and success.
23 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
24 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
25 Howard "Sonny" Turner.
